# threeDContent

**Type Property**

A base type that represents 3D content.

## Declaration

```swift
static var threeDContent: UTType { get }
```

## Discussion

The identifier for this type is `public.3d-content`.

This type conforms to [doc://com.apple.uniformtypeidentifiers/documentation/UniformTypeIdentifiers/UTTypeContent].

## 3D content

- **usd**: A type that represents Universal Scene Description content.
- **usdz**: A type that represents Universal Scene Description Package content.
